data.description: Welcome to beach living at its finest in Destin, Florida. This charming property offers a perfect blend of coastal elegance and modern comfort, making it an ideal retreat for residents and visitors alike. Make this your forever home or established rental investment. This beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom brick home is nestled in the sought-after Sunsail neighborhood and just a short stroll or golf cart ride away from the beach, shopping, restaurants, and more. This residence boasts stunning curb appeal with lush landscaping and a well-maintained exterior. The inside is stunning, with an open-concept featuring vaulted ceilings and hand-scraped wood look porcelain tile, offering a warm and inviting atmosphere. The upgraded moldings, fixtures, and finishes throughout add a touch of sophistication to every corner of the home. The interior features spacious living areas designed for both relaxation and entertainment. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, providing a wonderful flow for everyday living or hosting gatherings with family and friends. The completely remodeled kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring solid wood cabinetry with 42-inch upper cabinets, soft close drawers/doors, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The farmhouse sink and upgraded range hood, make this kitchen a must-see. The master suite is a haven of relaxation and privacy that features a beautiful bathroom with a furniture-style double vanity and marble countertop. The tub/ shower combo and toilet have a separate door for extra privacy. There is also spacious walk-in closet that makes getting dressed a breeze. The 2 additional bedrooms are spacious and well-appointed, sharing the hall bath with an extra-wide vanity with a custom granite countertop and a vessel sink. Step outside to discover your own private oasis, complete with a landscaped backyard and patio area perfect for outdoor dining and relaxing.
